#. (itstool) path: component/name
#: org.kde.ktimer.appdata.xml:6
msgid "KTimer"
msgstr "KTimer"

#. (itstool) path: component/summary
#: org.kde.ktimer.appdata.xml:7
msgid "Countdown Launcher"
msgstr "Lanceator de computo a retro"

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.ktimer.appdata.xml:9
msgid ""
"KTimer is a little tool to execute programs after some time. It allows you "
"to enter several tasks and to set a timer for each of them. The timers for "
"each task can be started, stopped, changed, or looped."
msgstr ""
"KTimer es un parve instrumento qu executa programmas post alcu tempore. Illo "
"permitte que tu inserta multe cargas e fixa un timer per omne de illos. Le "
"timers per cata carga pote esser startate, stoppate, modificate o repetite "
"in loop."

